[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Bedrock Guardrail for restricted-topic filtering. Configure
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # in the Bedrock console with restricted topics for off-care-
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # plan-treatment-recommendation, drug-prescription-attempted,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    165[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # new-condition-diagnosis-attempted, and off-protocol clinical
