[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2751[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Step 7: Persist the Durable Coaching-Decision Record and Longitudinal Updates
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2752[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2753[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The conversation log captures the dialog. The coaching-decision-record journal captures, separately, every coaching decision (escalation events, biometric-threshold events, behavior-change-stage updates, care-plan-deviation events, recommendation-with-citation events) with version stamps. The longitudinal store is updated with any new disclosures, preference changes, or context the conversation revealed.
