[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2765[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     its own Lambda with idempotency keys; the demo runs them
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2766[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     sequentially.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2767[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2768[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     care_plan = longitudinal_context["care_plan"]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2769[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     longitudinal = longitudinal_context["longitudinal"]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2770[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
